| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4268 — Recovery Inhibition (8base)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: d4d6d6c0-ec8f-503d-92a8-e3ded4f7f3b7"
